{"tid":891320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"活吞蛞蝓癱瘓8年！男臨終前對媽說「3字」病逝","createTime":"2018-11-06T04:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T08:24:55.000Z","uid":22876,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"58fbd29f8a4fb54c300cf0bd1d939c39f2f57e60","tid":891320,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpLTS8Ot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpLTS8Ot.jpg&h=1417e93b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲男子巴拉德（Sam Ballard），19歲時他在一場狂歡派對中為了接受朋友的挑戰，活吞從花園裡抓來的蛞蝓，結果導致他終身癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕澳洲男子巴拉德（Sam Ballard），19歲時他在一場狂歡派對中為了接受朋友的挑戰，活吞從花園裡抓來的蛞蝓，結果導致他終身癱瘓，需要別人24小時的全天候照料。最近他在告訴照顧他多年的母親「我愛妳」，之後不久就去世，巴拉德2日因為併發症過世，得年28歲。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpKUVBZs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpKUVBZs.jpg&h=8e6f1438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2010年，巴拉德在一次狂歡派對中喝了點紅酒，一名朋友慫恿他吃下從花園抓來的幾隻蛞蝓，「吃啊，看你敢不敢！」沒想到吃下蛞蝓後迅速暈倒，送至醫院急救後，被診斷出血液含有「廣東住血線蟲」（Rat Lungworm），隨後又被診斷出罹患嗜酸性腦膜炎（eosinophilic meningo-encephalitis），昏迷長達420天、四肢癱瘓，住院3年後才出院。<br />\n<br />\n巴拉德出院後無法自己行動，經常癲癇發作，身體無法自行控制體溫，並需要透過鼻胃管灌食，母親凱蒂（Katie Ballard）必須全天候照顧他。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，澳洲電視節目《The Sunday Project》主持人麗莎威爾金森（Lisa Wilkinson）透露，巴拉德上週五（2日）去世，守護在他身邊的是他的家人和愛他的人，他臨終前對母親說出最後一句話：「我愛妳」。"},{"pid":"4c9e23497e200fbdcf29f07e92a5c32c5e67a14a","tid":891320,"uid":85461,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"達爾文獎候選人"},{"pid":"ab1c2587f48279630732e34434c2ea82835cc5ed","tid":891320,"uid":130901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:31:40.000Z","msg":"最後都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7787ff8675284cd1410d48164fce58c36b096515","tid":891320,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:32:28.000Z","msg":"發現新大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9610cb9a416e71982da85a4baf25d6cca5534930","tid":891320,"uid":121473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b3b21f4b7d23781ee9aed6b5fff015b3f75f63","tid":891320,"uid":65774,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"又靚仔又識運動又係洋腸，咁靚首抽都要棄game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6340f68b4ffec6acab41ed883d7c86147f18e8","tid":891320,"uid":102179,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"d1b3b21f4b7d23781ee9aed6b5fff015b3f75f63","tid":891320,"uid":65774,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"又靚仔又識運動又係洋腸，咁靚首抽都要棄game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:35:47.000Z","msg":"亂鳩咁玩 哂左個AC"},{"pid":"6ec6ca9fcfff1bc7c54222ef36d804799fc81ee4","tid":891320,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1b3b21f4b7d23781ee9aed6b5fff015b3f75f63","tid":891320,"uid":65774,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"又靚仔又識運動又係洋腸，咁靚首抽都要棄game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"係佢自己要威先生吞蛞蝓"},{"pid":"06da80f4182424f6d889f44b76acb00af26a7f63","tid":891320,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"白痴仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410ff21bbb604fd6b5b6f83f6bd627c6f0bda412","tid":891320,"uid":130901,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"6ec6ca9fcfff1bc7c54222ef36d804799fc81ee4","tid":891320,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1b3b21f4b7d23781ee9aed6b5fff01